{% block content %}
<div class="hero general__hero hero--short">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <h1>About (R)evolution</h1>
        <p class="subtitle subtitle__single"><span>An epic day of adventure and exploration</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="general__hero-monster-dude about__hero-monster-dude"></div>
</div>
<div class="page-content about__content">
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="about__grid-row">
            <div class="about__blurb-grid-unit">
                <div class="about__blurb">
                    <h2>Shropshire's Original Web Conference</h2>
                    <p>This September, 250 people from just about every sort of digital job will join us in the 'Shire for a world-class, full-day web conference. Entrepreneurs, professionals and geeks of every description  will share what makes things faster, stronger, and better in the town of Darwin's birth. This is the (R)Evolution's 5th year, and we're proud to say: </p>

                    <p><strong>It keeps getting better!</strong></p>

                    <p>Our speakers represent many digital disciplines â€“ from design and user experience, to strategy and production. Each one brings years of experience and will share their unique perspective. </p>

                    <p>We have always been a friendly conference, because we started (and <a href="http://shropgeek.co.uk">continue</a>!) as a gathering of like-minded digital professionals over beer and discussion. There's a lot to fit into a single day, but we always make room for discussion and questions.</p>

                    <p>We believe in supporting the UK's digital community, and welcome anyone interested in the web.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about__image-grid-unit">
                <div class="about__image-twitter-box">
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/shropgeek" target="_blank">
                        <h3>Follow @shropgeek on Twitter</h3>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <img src="/assets/img/about-blurb-img.jpg" alt="Previous conference photo">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
